#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:5
msgid "Bend"
msgstr "弯曲"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:7
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst
msgid "Mode:     Object and Edit Modes"
msgstr "模式:     物体和编辑模式"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst
msgid ""
"Menu:     :menuselection:`Object/Mesh/Curve/Surface --> Transform --> "
"Bend`"
msgstr "菜单:     :menuselection:`物体/网格/曲线/曲面 --> 变换 --> 弯曲`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst
msgid "Hotkey:   :kbd:`Shift-W`"
msgstr "快捷键:   :kbd:`Shift-W`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:16
msgid "Bend Transform with Clamp on and off."
msgstr "开启和关闭限制时的弯曲变换。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:18
msgid ""
"This tool rotates a line of selected elements forming an arc between the "
"mouse-cursor and the 3D-cursor."
msgstr "该工具通过旋转一长条选中元素，形成鼠标指针和3D游标之间的弧形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:22
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用法"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:24
msgid ""
"The *Bend* tool can be used in any case where you might want to bend a "
"shape in two with a gradual transition between both sides."
msgstr "*弯曲* 工具用于将形状弯曲为两端之间逐渐过渡的情况。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:27
msgid ""
"This may take a little getting used to, the basics are listed below "
"controls are noted here:"
msgstr "这可能需要稍作适应，控制的基础原理如下:"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:29
msgid "The initial position of the cursors define the axis to bend on."
msgstr "指针和游标的初始位置决定了旋转的轴线。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:30
msgid ""
"The distance of the mouse-cursor to the 3D-cursor controls how sharp the "
"bend will be."
msgstr "鼠标指针到3D游标的距离控制弯曲的锐利程度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:31
msgid ""
"The relative angle of the mouse-cursor to the initial axis defines the "
"bend angle."
msgstr "鼠标指针与初始轴线的相对相对角度决定弯曲角度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:33
msgid ""
"If this seems overly complicated, it's probably best to try the tool "
"where it becomes quickly apparent how the tool reacts to your input."
msgstr ""
"如果这过于复杂，最好亲自尝试一下，这样很快就能弄清楚该工具对输入的反应。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:36
msgid "Bend Angle"
msgstr "弯曲角度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:37
msgid "The amount of rotation."
msgstr "旋转量。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:38
msgid "Radius"
msgstr "半径"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:39
msgid "The sharpness of the bend."
msgstr "弯曲的锐利程度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:46
msgid "Clamp"
msgstr "限制"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:41
msgid ""
"Normally the arc turns through a clamped rotation angle with the "
"selected elements extended along a tangent line beyond that (see above "
"left). When the clamp is deactivated, the arc continues around aligning "
"the selected elements into a circle (right)."
msgstr ""
"通常弧形会在选中元素超出切线的角度停止(见上文左图)。当关闭限制后，弧线会"
"继续绕圆周变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:45
msgid ""
"When off :kbd:`Alt` all selected elements follow a circle, even when "
"outside the segment between the 3D cursor and the mouse."
msgstr ""
"当 :kbd:`Alt` 关闭限制后，所有选中元素沿圆周变形，即使是超出3D游标和鼠标"
"之间的部分。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:50
msgid ""
"Unlike most other transform modes, *Bend* is not effected by *Pivot "
"Point* or *Transform Orientation*, always using the View Plane instead."
msgstr ""
"与其他变换模式不同，*弯曲* 不受 *轴心点* 或 *变换坐标系* 影响，总是在视图"
"平面上变形。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:55
msgid ""
"You can turn the bend angle through multiple rotations potentially "
"forming a spiral shape."
msgstr "可以通过多次弯曲的旋转，形成螺旋形状。"
